{
  "texts": [
    "Analytical results for QAOA on weighted MaxCutWe now present the analytical results for QAOA applied to weighted MaxCut on largegirth regular graphs with i.i.d. edge weights.",
    "We begin by analyzing p = 1 in Section 4.1.",
    "QAOA energy for p = 1 is given by a simple trigonometric formula derived in [39,Theorem 7].",
    "We use this formula to derive globally-optimal QAOA parameters.",
    "The parameters we derive are optimal in expectation, with the expectation taken over the distribution of the edge weights."
  ]
}